title: Ep 142: Complicated Grieving with Kelly Mclane
description: This episode I have comedian Kelly Mclane in studio discussing the sudden death of her brother two years ago. We discuss complicated grieving - when the relationship with the deceased may not have been ideal. We get super deep on spirituality and life and all of it. GET YOUR LIFE!!
author: nadav@ymhstudios.com (Christina Pazsitzky)
